short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Help you manage your Youtube tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mynifold is a tool that helps you manage and control Youtube tabs on your browser windows. With Mynifold, you can easily control YouTube players across different windows, that saves your efforts in switching between windows, getting lost and distracted.
